Summary: triangle with purple lights on each corner
divs: sighting detailswhile working on a commercial shoot at mt wilson observatory i was photographing the los angeles city lights from the parking lot. nothing was seen while on the site by me or any of the 50+ crew members or upon initial review of these pictures. i reviewed the shots again 2 years later for another project and i found this interesting shape hanging in the sky. there is a second picture where only one of the corners is visible. shot on a canon 20d 17-40mm l series lens @ 28mm iso 1600 f 2.8 1\8 sec exposure
